of course, i could be reading, or something else equally productive, but...i am not.  because then i wouldnt be bored and therefore not updating my livejournal, and i need to do that so...yeah, no homework tonight.  sydney is on her way over, and i am glad, because i am so bored.  bored out of my mind.

...at updating livejournal!  day off today...and let me say, it is a fun day off.  whohoo.  worked a hungover double yesterday, and that was KICK ASS.  liz is now working at applebees with me, yay lizzy gumm!  i really dont have much to report, i just feel like i never have anything to say.  so yeah.  day off.  updating.  i love matt...the end!

so, my phone died while i was in austin for christmas, so if i owed you a call or you couldnt get a hold of me, thats why.  and of course, my charger is here in g-town, so it is charging right now.  christmas was good, family was good...dad found my bellybutton piercing but thats about all the bad stuff that happened.  and missing matt while he was in san antonio, of course.

i have to work tonight, and while i really dont want to, its cause i traded a shift to get tomorrow off (my girls are coming in!!) so i really dont mind.  i got a check on friday for 92 bucks and then 100 in christmas cash, so those are all bonuses.  time to take the kitties to the vet!

everything is wierd

and no, i dont think that is stupid

four days

i got incredably sick (again) so sick that i had to call everyone i knew to find a ride to the doctor, so sick that i had a 102.5 fever AFTER medicine. they took blood and did all kinds of tests...again...and have no clue what is wrong with me...still.  apparantly every week im just gonna get sick with uncontrollable fevers and severe body pains.

i have lost 5 pounds in the last week and a half.  dieters and fat people everywhere will want me dead.

they gave me prescription stregth iburophen that if i dont take fairly religiously every 6 hours my fever will shoot back up (believe me on this one, the whole up and down thing is what i did all weekend), and an antibiotic even though they dont think its bacterial, "just in case" i have something bacterial AND a virus.  

i missed call all this weekend and i feel terrible, i threw my guts up this morning (i think i irritated my stomach from all the medicine cause i cant really eat and my tummy doesnt like me right now) and my stomach hurt so bad i didnt go to class. which i cant really afford to do, but.  yeah.  i suck.

selfishly, i just want to be better not for class but so that i can enjoy a trip to london next week and get wasted and eat sushi and not worry about infecting everyone with some weird virus that has never existed before me.

i will call it:
Lauren's Sickness.
has a nice ring to it dont you think?

everything is still bizarre.
i am hoping this weekend i can sort through what is all on my mind.
i need my brother.
SAM.  COME HERE.  NOW.

one week and two days to london.  i should start getting all my shit together.
SWEET.
i am so excited to see jessica.  oh my god.  i can not FREAKING wait to see that girl.
plus we get almost two whole days to ourselves...we are having sushi for thanksgiving dinner.  who else in the world could i have sushi with for thanksgiving dinner?  no one.  its like too good to be true.

and you know what?  im riding the LONDON EYE.  cause i super want to.
and eating at camden town-cheap chinese food 4 eva!!
and going out to pubs for beer-good beer.  my mouth is watering.
and shopping on high street ken and at h & m.
i. can. not. wait.

i have had a headache for a week now.
i am quite afraid i am going to fail everything.
my moms last minute trip down helped but also showed me new problems.
there is no escape from your own life, i guess.

sorry to be so melodramatic, but i feel like shit and i have to go to lab.
so i am being pissy.

i really do not feel good.

i think everyone is worried cause i have been secluding myself a little.  i promise that this is what i need right now.  everyone has opinions and i just need to figure out, for once, what i really really want.

thank you for supporting me when i need you, and understanding that i need to be by myself sometimes lately.  i need some time to focus on school, cause otherwise i will fail this semester.  oops.

i love you, and you know who you are. (this isnt just for one person...its for all those people who i love)

I just had a terrible dream.  it was so real.  matt and i had bought a house, and we were exploring it, and it was huge, like 6 stories with ways to get on the roof and cool things under the house too.  and he says 'this house is like my heart-it has to be this big to hold all my love for you' so im all happy.  then im putting things up, and i find this closet that i havent seen before, so i open it, and all thats in it is this grey, rectangular lock box.  so i open it, and see the normal stuff you would see in a lock box, papers, pictures, a silver ring, then i move that stuff aside, and blayne is in there.  she pops out (an amazing feat considering the size of the lock box) and i say 'what are you doing here' and she says 'matt put me here'  and then  matt comes in and gets mad at me when i am like, why is this here?  and he says 'i always have to have a room to myself, what are you doing going in there, this is where i keep the things for just me, i gave you this whole house that is my heart, why cant i just have this one little corner to myself?'  and look up and there are dozens of boxes identical to the first one on the shelves.  and he says 'if you want to know absolutly everthing about me, you should just go now' so i wake up crying and get ready and when the alram goes off i get matt to bring me to school.  and now i cant stop crying.  i told him the dream but i dont think he understands how i feel about it-i feel like it happened yesterday, thast how real it was.  it wasnt like most of my dreams, it was like the dreams i had when i was a kid that came true sometimes.  not that i think blayne is gonna pop out of a box somewhere, but...thats what the dream was like.  i think he is mad at me for being upset.  but it was the scariest dream i ever had, including that one with cookie monster and the robbers.  do you guys think dreams mean things?

i hate how stupid bitches can ruin a good time.  ugh.  makes my skin crawl.

on the other hand, i love matt.  so everything is bueno.

my mom and her bf and daughter are coming into town today, so i have to be a busy bee and clean clean clean before they get here.  and im sure there will be a nice dinner tonight.  with wine.  and then the magic hour party where i fully intend to make out with matt in front of all of you.  with tounge.  and if you arent here to see it, then you should be jealous.  cause its gonna be hot.

next week is gonna suck school wise.  maybe my mom will just stay the whole week and help me.  like in high school!

GIRLS WHO ARE ABROAD:  promise me that when you get back, we can have a serious girl bonding night.  please?  jessica and liz and megan must reply.  sniff.



only bitches talk shit.

so, anytime i am doing ok, it seems like LIFE conspires against me.  i promise im not being melodramatic.  as soon as i get ok with school, i have to get fucking sick so that, not only do i fall behind, but i cant start work on my next week from hell (three tests, one presentation, three papers).  on top of that, my mom gets fired for no god damn reason other than her boss is a jerk off and cant admit that HE did something wrong.  so she is all depressed and i really want her to come down this weekend, but it is the one time i can work to keep from dying next week, plus there are all these parties taht i want to go to cause i never get to do anything cause i have the semester from hell.  oh, and helena-totally a boy.  the girl who gave her to us said she (he) was a girl, so we just went with that, until i happened to notice a ballsack yesterday.  funny how when you give a cat a pink collar and a girly name, you never bother to look at their genitals.  so thats kind of funny but also sad and makes me feel like a bad kitty mom, plus i have french work i UBER dont want to do and a quiz tomorrow.

and all that last rant-matt and i got into a huge fight, but absolutely nothing got resolved, i still have all this pent up emotion and i dont know how to tell him cause its never the right time.  i just love him so much, he is the best thing that ever happened to me, he is so sweet and takes such good care of me whenever i need him, but i feel so...i dont know.  i guess i have to bring it up and (once again) be the bad guy who just can be satisfied with what they have.

i just have no motivation for anything and i feel myself falling back into where i was earlier this semster and i hate it.  i just want it all to be over.  i am so sick of crying.

ex's.

im sorry, really i am, to anyone that reads this and doesnt agree, or has no clue what im talking about, or gets offended that i think this or put it on my livejournal, but i am so SICK and TIRED of feeling like i have to be fine with everything that has to do with ex girlfriends.  cause im NOT.  its a tricky subject anyway, but seriously.  when it gets to the point that we cant actually  mention thier names without it being some sort of SIN, and if we make a joke someone gets their feelings hurt, SOMETHING IS WRONG.

and you know what?  I CAN BE MAD IF I WANT TO.  it hurts my feelings the way that i am the one that has to keep bending over and fucking taking it cause we dont want to hurt someone else's feelings.  if i am the most important, then why dont i feel like it?  god forbid we hurt HER feelings.  since it is so important to keep HER happy.  I AM SO FUCKING FRUSTRATED RIGHT NOW.
